data.description: MLS# 271838 Welcome to 2804 S Tacoma St. located near Canyon Lakes golf community and all the major shopping amenities. Built in 2002 this home has been very well maintained and modernized with updates from inside-out.This pristine 3 bed, 2 bath rambler sits on a .30-acre corner lot, offering 1,414 sqft of spacious living. It features a convenient attached 2-car garage as well as a storage shed in the backyard. Park your Rv or boat next to your home with the addition parking. Fully fenced yard ensures privacy and a safe play area for family and friends. Abundant storage solutions make organization a breeze. Priced at $399,900. This home provides outstanding value. Don't miss the chance to own a property that blends space, comfort, and convenience. Make it your dream home today!
